Strategies to Avoid Race Conditions:

1. Use Mutexes (Locks)
2. Atomic Operations
3. Lock-Free Data Structures
4. Thread Synchronization
5. Immutable Data
6. Thread-Local Storages


Strategies to Avoid Deadlocks:

1. Lock Ordering
2. Lock Timeout
3. Lock Hierarchy
4. Avoid Nested Locks
5. Use Lock-Free Algorithms
6. Detect and Handle Deadlocks
7. Design for Simplicity
